The '''Widek Bypass''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]] located in the [[Farlax sector/Legends|Farlax sector]]. The route was in fact a continuation of [[Metellos Trade Route/Legends|Metellos Trade Route]] from its terminus at [[Orooturoo]]. The Bypass was named because the route bypassed the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]], passing through [[Wehttam]], [[Thobek]], and [[Galantos]], before terminating at [[Widek]].

